  ('SUB_1990', 'Kitchen Accessories', 'CAT_1990', 'Straining is an everyday task in most kitchens, for which a tough, durable, easy-to-clean and maintain strainer is a necessity. Crafted from high grade and food grade stainless steel, it can be used for strain soup, juice, milk, tea, and other liquids. Strong, sturdy and durable, it is rust, crack and stain resistant.¬†The innovative design prevents spillage while pouring and filtering. The strainer is a heavy duty which is suitable for both home and commercial use. They are resistant to rust and easy to store.'),
  ('SUB_1991', 'Pet Food & Accessories', 'CAT_1991', 'They Help Remove Tartar, Build Stronger Teeth And Act As Theethers For Puppies'),
  ('SUB_1992', 'Masalas & Spices', 'CAT_1992', 'Everest presents their authentic range of masalas that are blended with a wide variety of handpicked and selected spices that bring a whole new flavour and meaning to your dishes. Rake up your favourite recipes and cuisines by adding this magical blend of Everest masalas.'),
  ('SUB_1993', 'Organic Staples', 'CAT_1993', 'Flaxseeds are a great source of dietary fibre flaxseeds are loaded with two essential fatty acids, omega-3 and omega-6 flaxseeds are low in starch and sugar, hence they are not high on calories eating them regularly is good for your health.'),
  ('SUB_1994', 'Bins & Bathroom Ware', 'CAT_1994', 'These are multipurpose baskets that are sturdy and easy to handle. These are easy to carry and are perfect to keep your home or office clean. These can also be used as a dustbin to keep the place free from scrap. Use it anywhere in your house or in the office or else even while going for a picnic or just as per your need to keep the area scrap-free. Stack these beautiful and coloured baskets to use it anytime, anywhere.'),
  ('SUB_1995', 'Health & Medicine', 'CAT_1995', 'This Hot Water Bag ensures that the heat reaches the affected region, bringing relief from pain. For use, fill the bag with hot water and place it in the region of pain and the effect can be felt in minutes. It can be used as a natural body warmer and also for heat therapy treatment. It is useful in case of joint pains, muscular cramps, menstrual pains, muscle pull, stomach and backaches, arthritis and rheumatic pains, bed warmer, sports aches and pains.'),
  ('SUB_1996', 'Steel Utensils', 'CAT_1996', 'Joyo Klip It Stainless steel container comes with easy locking. These containers are made from high quality non-magnetic stainless steel body. Joyo Klip It container has odourless lid cover with food-grade silicone seal (gasket) in lid & has all 4 sides locks which ensure airtight containers for keeping food fresh, 100% leak-proof containers for keeping food from spilling, stackable design for easily storing the containers on top of each other and the pioneering clip mechanism. Take this container to the office, school, camping or hiking.'),
  ('SUB_1997', 'Skin Care', 'CAT_1997', 'Pond''s men pimple clear facewash designed for the trendy men of today. Ideal for those with oily skin and perfect as a daily use face wash. Enriched with mineral clay which will help remove that excess oil from your face without leaving it too dry. With a breakthrough lock and clean technology, this facewash locks onto the pimple-causing germs and helps clear them.¬†It‚Äôs special patented thymo-t formula will help you reduce your pimples and you will be able to see visible results in 3 days. It gently removes the excess oil from your face without leaving it too dry. The face wash unclogs your pores to provide you smooth and silky skin and is enriched with mineral clay which helps reduce oil and acne breakout. Rejuvenate your skin with the active ingredients of this pimple clear face wash and watch the results.¬†Created by pond''s, the skin care experts, a face wash that will help fight pimples and leave your skin feeling cool and refreshed. No more avoiding people because of that sudden breakout just carry your handy solution to a clear pimple free skin. Recommended using twice a day (morning and night), for best result use the pond''s men oil control face cream after the facewash.'),
  ('SUB_1998', 'Men''s Grooming', 'CAT_1998', 'Cinthol Deostick is a deodorant like you have never tried before. Made from cream formulation, not spray, it lasts 3 times longer than ordinary deo''s and is gentle on your skin too. Use it after shower to experience that awesome feeling all day long.'),
  ('SUB_1999', 'Men''s Grooming', 'CAT_1999', 'Own the day and refresh your imagination. With zesty lime top notes, a refreshing heart of green apple and a sharp vetiver base, the masculine signature scent of New York For Him is as distinctive and diverse as its namesake, fresh aromatic signature scent.'),
  ('SUB_2000', 'Steel Utensils', 'CAT_2000', 'Duo Star Lunch box from Signoraware brings you an uber chic range of steel lunchbox with a plastic outer body that is high on style and does not compromise on any health and safety standards. These tough and spill-proof make them easier to carry for metro/bus commuters. The specially designed lid with grooves prevents the mixing of food within the compartmentalised container.');
